description: Join us on the last Friday of every month at Chit Hole Phuket for a relaxed Bitcoin meetup! Join our Telegram group now to engage with the local Bitcoin community!

name: Columbus Bitcoin
description: Columbus Bitcoin is a monthly social gathering centered around Bitcoin. Our goal is to exchange stories related to Bitcoin, provide technical insights, foster business connections, and build lasting friendships. Regardless of whether you're just dipping your toes into the complex world of Bitcoin, struggling with its jargon, or you're a seasoned veteran who was involved in drafting the initial Bitcoin white paper in 2009, everyone is invited to learn and share their experiences.

Cleveland Bitcoin
description: The Cleveland Bitcoin Club has public, free meetups twice a month. One is typically a bar/social meetup and another is an education/demonstration/planning type meetup at a Public Library. Cleveland Bitcoin hosted the 2024 Halving Party at Town Hall in Ohio City in April 2024 with 60+ attendees and several vendors who accept Bitcoin attended. All are welcome - Bitcoin only.
